Another ANC Councillor has been shot and killed in Mzumikhulu, KwaZulu-Natal.Police spokesperson Thembeka Mbhele confirmed on Wednesday.&#8221; Wiseman Mduduzi Shibase (39) was shot dead at 6:30pm on Tuesday while he was trying to get inside his car,&#8221; she saidMbhele added that cause of the shooting is not yet known but the provincial task team is investigating the matter.More to follow as story develops.TNA Reporter 